#. module: dropshipping
#: model_terms:ir.ui.view,arch_db:dropshipping.welcome_article_body
msgid ""
"<strong>Automated Sales Funnels</strong> – Maximize conversions with the "
"<strong>Marketing Automation App</strong>, guiding potential buyers "
"seamlessly from interest to purchase."
msgstr ""
"<strong>Automatiserede salgstrager</strong> – Maksimér konverteringer med "
"<strong>automatiseret marketing</strong>, der guider potentielle kunder "
"problemfrit fra interesse til køb."

#. module: dropshipping
#: model_terms:ir.ui.view,arch_db:dropshipping.welcome_article_body
msgid ""
"<strong>Email Campaigns That Convert</strong> – Use the <strong>Email "
"Marketing App</strong> to send newsletters, promotions, and updates straight "
"to your customers' inboxes."
msgstr ""
"<strong>E-mailkampagner, der fungerer</strong> – Brug <strong>E-"
"mailmarketingappen</strong> til at sende nyhedsbreve, kampagner og "
"opdateringer direkte til dine kunders indbakker."

#. module: dropshipping
#: model_terms:ir.ui.view,arch_db:dropshipping.ir_ui_view_1661
msgid ""
"<strong>Find the perfect case for your phone – durable, stylish, and built "
"for everyday life.</strong>"
msgstr ""
"<strong>Find det perfekte cover til din smartphone – robust, stilfuldt og "
"designet til hverdagsbrug.</strong>"

#. module: dropshipping
#: model_terms:ir.ui.view,arch_db:dropshipping.ir_ui_view_1661
msgid "<strong>Japanese collection</strong>"
msgstr "<strong>Japansk samling</strong>"

#. module: dropshipping
#: model_terms:ir.ui.view,arch_db:dropshipping.welcome_article_body
msgid ""
"<strong>One-Click Confirmation:</strong> Review and confirm purchase orders "
"instantly."
msgstr ""
"<strong>Bekræftelse med ét klik:</strong> Gennemse og bekræft indkøbsordrer "
"med det samme."

#. module: dropshipping
#: model_terms:ir.ui.view,arch_db:dropshipping.welcome_article_body
msgid ""
"<strong>Seamless Supplier Communication:</strong> Send orders to your "
"supplier in just one click, ensuring smooth and timely fulfillment."
msgstr ""
"<strong>Problemfri leverandørkommunikation:</strong> Send ordrer til din "
"leverandør med ét enkelt klik, og sikr dermed en problemfri og rettidig "
"udførelse."

#. module: dropshipping
#: model_terms:ir.ui.view,arch_db:dropshipping.welcome_article_body
msgid ""
"<strong>Social Media Made Simple</strong> – Schedule and manage posts "
"effortlessly with the <strong>Social Marketing App</strong> to keep your "
"audience engaged."
msgstr ""
"<strong>Gør arbejdet med sociale medier nemt</strong> – Planlæg og "
"administrer nemt indlæg med <strong>appen til markedsføring på sociale "
"medier</strong> for at begejstre dit publikum."

